  Update Model Permissions

› 1. Read Only (current)        Codex can read files in the current workspace.
                                Approval is required to edit files or access
                                the internet.
  2. Ask for approval           Codex can read and edit files in the current
                                workspace, and run commands. Approval is
                                required to access the internet or edit other
                                files.
  3. Cool Read Write (current)  Codex can read and write files within the
                                workspace and execute commands, but will never
                                read or write files outside the workspace. No
                                internet access. (Designed for safety)
  4. Full Access                Codex can edit files outside this workspace
                                and access the internet without asking for
                                approval. Exercise caution when using.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
